"┌ conversations ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐"
"│Conversations stream                                                                                                                                                                                  │"
"│                                                                                                                                                                                                      │"
"│When connected via a daemon socket, this tab shows per-pane last prompt and assistant excerpts (newest-first, Pi streaming partials folded).                                                          │"
"│                                                                                                                                                                                                      │"
"│Current read mode: file-watcher. Conversation excerpts require the daemon's pi-bridge / claude-channel / oc subscribers. Start the daemon with `flightdeck-dashboard daemon start --session <name>`   │"
"│and relaunch the TUI with `--socket <path>`.                                                                                                                                                          │"
